            <thetext>Opera 10 (Mac / Windows) has a bug which causes the whole browser to crash:

try {
  var e = new Error();
  e.message = &quot;&quot;;
  throw e;
} catch (e) {
   alert(e.message);
}

We changed the default error message of BaseError from an empty string to &quot;error&quot; (r19978) which fixed the problem for the framework.</thetext>
